}}Hardwood Acres has a population of 611, with 207 households and an average of 3 persons per household. The median age is 39.4, with 70% of the population being between the ages of 18 and 64. The median household income is $109,196. 3.4% of the population is below the poverty line.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Census profile: Hardwood Acres, MI |url=http://censusreporter.org/profiles/16000US2636585-hardwood-acres-mi/ |access-date=2026-05-08 |website=Census Reporter |language=en}}</ref>

